{"title":"Found: Polar Grit X Pro offers better tracking for bigger adventures","link":"https://bikerumor.com/found-polar-grit-x-pro-offers-better-tracking-for-bigger-adventures/","date":1639066829000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07092117/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-Feature.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"525\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07092117/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-Feature-800x525.jpg\" alt=\"Polar Grit X Pro Feature\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07092117/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-Feature-800x525.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07092117/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-Feature-297x195.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07092117/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-Feature-120x79.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07092117/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-Feature-768x504.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07092117/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-Feature-1536x1008.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07092117/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-Feature.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-280211\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>If you’ve had issues with smartwatches not being able to handle everything you throw at them, the <a href=\"https://www.polar.com/us-en/grit-x-pro?utm_source=GearJunkie&amp;utm_medium=Custom_Article&amp;utm_campaign=GearJunkie_Promo&amp;utm_content=031221\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Polar Grit X Pro</a> is here to change that.</p><p>The Grit X Pro is designed to be a combo fitness tracker and outdoor watch, with tracking modes for cycling, surfing, skiing, or hiking and turn by turn GPS capability.</p><p>The Titan Edition uses titanium for a much lighter version with the same durability and performance, so you don’t have to worry about all those features weighing you down.</p><div id=\"attachment_280217\"><p><a href=\"https://www.polar.com/us-en/grit-x-pro?utm_source=GearJunkie&amp;utm_medium=Custom_Article&amp;utm_campaign=GearJunkie_Promo&amp;utm_content=031221\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-280217\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07080013/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-1.jpg\" alt=\"Polar Grit X Pro 1\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07080013/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-1.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07080013/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-1-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07080013/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-1-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07080013/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-1-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07080013/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-1-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-280217\">Photo/Polar</p></div><h2>Let’s Talk Features…</h2><p><strong>Precision Prime:</strong> Let’s face it, it can be difficult to keep an accurate heart rate measurement when you’re constantly in motion, not to mention if you have a darker skin tone and the typical single light tech in most watches isn’t quite accurate.</p><p>That is where Polar Precision Prime tech comes in. It combines multiple sensor technologies including optical heart rate measurement to give a more thorough and accurate heart rate reading.</p><p><strong>FuelWise &amp; Training Load Pro:&nbsp;</strong>Whether you’re the type to forget to refuel your body or you just want to make sure to pack exactly what you need to keep yourself going on a long ride, FuelWise uses your calorie expenditures to give you periodical reminders that it is time to smash some carbs or grab a drink.</p><p>Training Load Pro helps prevent injury by helping you track the load placed on your cardiovascular and musculoskeletal systems during activity to help observe and not exceed your body’s limits.</p><p>On top of these standouts, there are tons of other dope features and functions including sleep tracking, performance and recovery tests, GPS, always-on outdoor dashboards, and more.</p><div id=\"attachment_280221\"><p><a href=\"https://www.polar.com/us-en/grit-x-pro?utm_source=GearJunkie&amp;utm_medium=Custom_Article&amp;utm_campaign=GearJunkie_Promo&amp;utm_content=031221\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-280221\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07082634/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-2.jpg\" alt=\"Polar Grit X Pro 2\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07082634/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-2.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07082634/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-2-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07082634/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-2-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07082634/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-2-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07082634/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-2-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-280221\">Photo/Polar</p></div><h2><strong>Go Confidently Into the Unknown</strong></h2><p>This watch has several tools to help you find your way.</p><p><strong>Turn by Turn Guidance:</strong> This feature allows you to use <a href=\"https://www.komoot.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">komoot</a> to plan your routes and then sync them with your watch so you have accurate navigation on the go.</p><p><strong>Track Back:</strong> Track Back functions as your trail of breadcrumbs so that you can find your way back to where you began, no matter how far off the beaten path you wander.</p><p><strong>Global Navigation Satellite Systems:&nbsp;</strong>The GPS in this watch works in tandem with global satellite systems to ensure that you have the most accurate GPS positioning as well as greater signal access and faster fixes.</p><div id=\"attachment_280228\"><p><a href=\"https://www.polar.com/us-en/grit-x-pro?utm_source=GearJunkie&amp;utm_medium=Custom_Article&amp;utm_campaign=GearJunkie_Promo&amp;utm_content=031221\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-280228\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07090401/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-3.jpg\" alt=\"Polar Grit X Pro 3\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07090401/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-3.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07090401/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-3-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07090401/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-3-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07090401/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-3-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07090401/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-3-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-280228\">Photo/Polar</p></div><h2>Let’s Talk Hardware…</h2><p>The watch face is made with ultra-strong scratch-resistant sapphire glass. The durability was tested under military-grade conditions including extreme temperatures, drop testing, sand and dust exposure, and more. It is water-resistant up to 100m. Impressive battery life allows 40-100 hours in training mode and up to 7 days in watch mode on a single charge.</p><div id=\"attachment_280230\"><p><a href=\"https://www.polar.com/us-en/grit-x-pro?utm_source=GearJunkie&amp;utm_medium=Custom_Article&amp;utm_campaign=GearJunkie_Promo&amp;utm_content=031221\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-280230\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07091821/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-4.jpg\" alt=\"Polar Grit X Pro 4\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07091821/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-4.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07091821/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-4-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07091821/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-4-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07091821/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-4-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/07091821/Polar-Grit-X-Pro-4-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-280230\">Photo/Polar</p></div></section></article></div></div>","author":"Sponsored Post","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"884b80628a4d24ace3e46a6644446fc62c1912b743af16a4a6513eb736299585","category":"Cycling"}